The New Year can be a breath of fresh air for so many of us...but before you take on 2021, will you take just a moment to watch this video?
•
No matter how your baby came to you...
What your journey has looked like...
Or how old they are now...
You matter too.
•
Your needs and heart and dreams matter.
•
We are so used to giving 110% of ourselves that we sometimes forget that we as parents are so important. Honoring ourselves and what we need is important. 
•
Will you tag a friend who needs to hear this? And if you're looking for extra support and resources to help guide you through another year of parenthood, we've got you. 💕⁣
